'''Rodrik Cassel''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first]] and [[Season 2|second]] seasons. He is played by guest star [[Ron Donachie]] and debuts in the [[Winter is Coming (episode)|series premiere]]. Ser Rodrik Cassel is [[Master-at-Arms]] at [[Winterfell]] and a loyal servant to [[House Stark]]. Even in his old age he is still a skilled warrior. He was executed by [[Theon Greyjoy]] during the [[fall of Winterfell]].

